---
description: Build toward the hackathon rubric
alwaysApply: true
---

The implementation should optimize for the hackathon rubric:

1. Challenge fit
2. Quality and design
3. Originality and impact
4. Commercialisation potential
5. Bright Data bonus only if safe

When making tradeoffs:
- choose stronger challenge fit over extra features
- choose stable demo over clever complexity
- choose cleaner repo over broader scope
- choose user value over technical novelty
